snippet.title: Poppi - Global Game Jam 2020 Trailer
snippet.description:
Oh no, the sky is falling down, and only Poppi can fix using its rainbow jetpack! Place the falling pieces and ascend to Space and beyond.

Made for Global Game Jam 2020 (Málaga Site) with the theme Repair.

You can play on: https://poppitos.itch.io/poppi
